    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert hiring manager and resume evaluator.\n\nAnalyze the following candidate resume for the role: {{$json.role}} \nMake sure one of the candidates is strong.\n\nResume Text:\n{{$json.text}}\n\nEvaluation Instructions:\n\n* If the role is SWE:\n  Evaluate technical skills, programming languages, frameworks, software engineering capability, problem solving ability, and projects.\n\n* If the role is BDM:\n  Evaluate communication, sales ability, negotiation skills, business growth capability, leadership, and client handling.\n\nScoring Rules:\n\n* Strong candidates: score 8-10\n* Average candidates: score 5-7\n* Weak candidates: score below 5\n\nClassification Rules:\n\n* Score >= 8 → Strong\n* Score >= 5 and < 8 → Average\n* Score < 5 → Weak\n\nIMPORTANT RULES:\n\n* Return ONLY valid raw JSON\n* Do NOT use markdown\n* Do NOT wrap response inside ```json\n* Do NOT include explanations outside JSON\n* Escape all quotation marks properly\n* Ensure valid JSON formatting\n\nReturn response in EXACTLY this format:\n\n{\n\"ai_score\": 0,\n\"classification\": \"\",\n\"summary\": \"\",\n\"strengths\": \"\",\n\"concerns\": \"\",\n\"interview_recommendation\": \"\"\n}\n",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        1776,
        -256
      ],
      "id": "f2617447-aab8-4c00-8f25-7fec36783757",
      "name": "AI Agent",
      "executeOnce": false,
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
